---
import PublicLayout from '../layouts/PublicLayout.astro';
import { FaBolt, FaLeaf, FaUsers, FaAward, FaGlobe, FaHeart } from 'react-icons/fa';
---

<PublicLayout title="About Us - EcoRide" description="Learn about EcoRide's mission to revolutionize transportation with sustainable electric vehicle solutions.">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-secondary-50 py-20">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center">
                <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
                    Driving the Future of
                    <span class="text-primary-600">Sustainable Transportation</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                    At EcoRide, we believe that sustainable transportation shouldn't mean compromising on quality,
                    performance, or convenience. We're here to prove that electric is better.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Mission Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                        We're on a mission to make sustainable transportation accessible to everyone.
                        By providing premium electric vehicles for rent, we're helping reduce carbon emissions
                        while offering an exceptional driving experience.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                        Every mile driven with EcoRide is a step towards a cleaner, healthier planet.
                        We believe that small actions can create big changes, and together, we can drive
                        the transformation to a sustainable future.
                    </p>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                        <div class="text-center">
                            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-2">10,000+</div>
                            <div class="text-gray-600">Happy Customers</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-center">
                            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-2">50,000+</div>
                            <div class="text-gray-600">Miles Driven</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <img
                            src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3764119/pexels-photo-3764119.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800"
                            alt="Electric vehicle charging"
                            class="w-full h-auto rounded-2xl shadow-xl"
                    />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Values Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Values</h2>
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                    These core values guide everything we do and shape our commitment to you and the environment.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                    <div class="bg-primary-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
                        <FaLeaf className="h-8 w-8 text-primary-600" />
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Sustainability</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">
                        We're committed to reducing environmental impact through clean transportation solutions.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                    <div class="bg-secondary-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
                        <FaAward className="h-8 w-8 text-secondary-600" />
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Excellence</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">
                        We maintain the highest standards in vehicle quality, customer service, and user experience.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                    <div class="bg-accent-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
                        <FaUsers className="h-8 w-8 text-accent-600" />
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Community</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">
                        We build strong relationships with our customers and contribute positively to local communities.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                    <div class="bg-primary-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
                        <FaBolt className="h-8 w-8 text-primary-600" />
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Innovation</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">
                        We embrace cutting-edge technology to provide the best electric vehicle experience.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                    <div class="bg-secondary-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
                        <FaGlobe className="h-8 w-8 text-secondary-600" />
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Accessibility</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">
                        We make sustainable transportation accessible and affordable for everyone.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                    <div class="bg-accent-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
                        <FaHeart className="h-8 w-8 text-accent-600" />
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Care</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">
                        We care deeply about our customers, our planet, and the future we're building together.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Team or Story Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
                <div>
                    <img
                            src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3184418/pexels-photo-3184418.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800"
                            alt="Team working together"
                            class="w-full h-auto rounded-2xl shadow-xl"
                    />
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Story</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                        Founded in 2020 by a team of environmental enthusiasts and tech innovators,
                        EcoRide started with a simple vision: make electric vehicle rental as easy
                        and accessible as traditional car rentals.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                        What began as a small fleet of five electric vehicles has grown into a
                        comprehensive network serving thousands of customers across multiple cities.
                        We've proven that sustainable doesn't mean sacrificing quality or convenience.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                        Today, we continue to expand our fleet, improve our technology, and work
                        towards our goal of making every urban journey emission-free.
                    </p>
                    <a href="/contact" class="bg-primary-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors font-semibold">
                        Get in Touch
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-primary-600">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
                Join Our Mission
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-primary-100 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Be part of the sustainable transportation revolution. Every rental helps build a cleaner future.
            </p>
            <a href="/signup" class="bg-white text-primary-600 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors font-semibold">
                Start Your Journey
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>
</PublicLayout>